<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="overall-adv">overall <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌəʊvər'ɔːl/    美 /ˌoʊvər'ɔːl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>总共；[句子副词] 总的说来</strong></h4>
<p>when you consider everything; generally：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Overall, this is a very useful book.
总的来说，这是一本很有用的书。</p></div></div>